OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for Shetland
OL,6,Fwith some light rain or drizzle,
OL,7,Fotherwise a mixture of bright or sunny
OL,8,Fintervals and scattered light showers.
OL,9,FModerate to fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mixture of sunny then clear
OL,12,Fspells and a few passing showers.
OL,13,FWinds a moderate to fresh
OL,14,Fsouthwesterly veering westerly.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FOrkney mainly dry with some
OL,17,Fsunny spells and just the odd shower.
OL,18,FShetland will see more in the way of
OL,19,Fshowers. Light to moderate breeze.
OL,20,FColder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
