OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright,
OL,6,Fshowery start on Sunday, perhaps
OL,7,Fwintry over Shetland, then cloudy with
OL,8,Frain. Drier and brighter on Monday
OL,9,Fthen showery and breezy on Tuesday.
